title: Muthu (1995)
description: The story is set in a Zamindar's palace. Just like in Velaikaran, Rajni Zamindar Sarath Babu's loyal servant. In a village drama, Meena catches Sarath's eye but a turn of circumstances forces Rajni to take Meena back home. They are stuck for a while in Kerala and romance blossoms. develops between Sarat and Rajni and Rajni is sent away from the palace while mysteriously another Senior Rajni turns up.
